reviews.title: Would play in my sleep if I could...
reviews.comment: Very addictive fun game. I love codes. Challenges your brain. Sometimes they\'re easy some are tough and a couple have not made sense to me, but all-in-all an above average to exvellent game. Would rate 5 stars but  there is always room for improvement (nothing against the game), so I\'ll give it a written 4 1/2. Try it you\'ll love it & wont want to put it down!!!
